research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Watauga City, TX, include the Mayor and seven Council Members. Cris Blackburn holds both the Mayor Pro Tem and Council Member Place 2 roles. There was a discrepancy for Place 5, with the official city website listing it as vacant, while Tarrant County and the TML City Officials Directory list Malissa Minucci. The information from Tarrant County was last modified in September 2025, and the TML directory also lists Malissa Minucci, so Malissa Minucci has been included for Place 5.

office.name: Council Member - Mayor Pro Tempore - Place 2
